{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a traditional Passover with the second set of dishes and-- and-- and we'd clean all the bread out and went through the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we had really, really-- to this day I know my [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know it because I used to practice it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "God forbid, my grandfather would-- would catch me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I used to know it by heart, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So because that was-- I was the youngest, I had to say it, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But beautiful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then one of my uncles used to come there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it's kind of interesting because he worked for my other uncle, who had a tailor-- clothing factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was a bachelor and since was always going with Gentile girls, he was not allowed to go to my other uncle for Passover so he would always come-- because she said, you can come, but you've got to leave the girl-- the shikse behind.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so he always came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We always had room for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He came there with his girlfriend and-- and she was a very nice lady.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and unfortunately, he did not survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so-- so we had a beautiful Passover.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We even-- we celebrated Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We went to the-- you know, I'm talking about 1935, 1936, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father with that high hat and that dark tailcoat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and we had fairly good seats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember Yom Kippur we had locks, we had-- where the books were locked in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he always brought that sandwich for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "After 12 o'clock I could eat on Yom Kippur that sandwich, but I had to go way out from the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so we had-- I-- I-- [INAUDIBLE] a typical Jewish home, you know, a modern Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
